      <title>英伟达股价下跌，交易员放弃看涨期权押注</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/nvidia-sees-wave-of-call-option-sales-as-stock-drops-from-record</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于英伟达公司 (Nvidia Corp.) 股价在创下 11 月以来首次历史新高后出现下跌，投资者周二抛售大量该股看涨期权。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/nvidia-sees-wave-of-call-option-sales-as-stock-drops-from-record</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 Jan 2025 17:42:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
