      <title>凯雷对大型科技公司持谨慎态度，看好“极其便宜”的欧洲</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/carlyle-cautious-on-big-tech-likes-exceptionally-cheap-europe</link>
      <description><![CDATA[凯雷集团的杰森托马斯表示，美国大型科技股的上涨开始显得过度，提升了陷入困境的欧洲股市的吸引力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/carlyle-cautious-on-big-tech-likes-exceptionally-cheap-europe</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 Jan 2025 17:40:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国减少网络内容 暴力极端主义依然猖獗</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/us-pulls-back-from-disrupting-violent-extremism-on-social-media</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据现任和前任美国官员以及互联网极端主义专家称，美国联邦调查局和国土安全部在过去两年中已经减少了打击暴力极端分子网络活动的力度，他们担心在即将上任的特朗普政府领导下，这种趋势将会加速。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/us-pulls-back-from-disrupting-violent-extremism-on-social-media</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 Jan 2025 15:37:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Meta 裁减事实核查人员，称内容删除“过分”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/meta-cuts-fact-checkers-after-content-moderation-went-too-far</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Meta Platforms Inc. 将终止在美国社交媒体平台上的第三方事实核查，转而允许用户使用社区笔记系统对帖子的准确性进行评论，该公司表示这将促进言论自由。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/meta-cuts-fact-checkers-after-content-moderation-went-too-far</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 Jan 2025 13:50:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Nvidia 发布后股价下跌，投资者仍意犹未尽</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/nvidia-ceo-unveils-more-powerful-graphics-cards-at-ces-event</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英伟达公司 (Nvidia Corp.) 首席执行官黄仁勋 (Jensen Huang) 的广泛产品演示未能推动这家人工智能芯片制造商迈向新的高度，导致该公司股价周二下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/nvidia-ceo-unveils-more-powerful-graphics-cards-at-ces-event</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 Jan 2025 03:12:38 GMT</pubDate>
